column5: Just got back from Walmart in Oshawa (north end) and they have fishing items on clearance. Including lindy darters!!!(only 2 left where I was) If you want to save your self 6 bucks I'd go before they are all sold out! Also have gulp alive maggots and fish fry mini containers for 5 bucks!
Thanks for the heads up will check them out tomorrow
I got a couple of those Gulp containers at the Kitchener store a month ago for $5 as well.
Lindy Darters for $3 is a great deal...thanks for posting!
